Package io.github.eutro.wasm2j.api

package io.github.eutro.wasm2j.api
A configurable API over the less stable and lower-level core Wasm2j API.

The main entrypoint to this API is the WasmCompiler, to which WebAssembly modules can be submitted for compilation.

The compiler can be configured using the events API.
